  Codex review: keeping this open for maintainer follow-up; there is still a little grit to resolve. _Reviewed May 30,                                          
  2026, 10:28 PM ET / 02:28 UTC._                                                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                
  Summary                                                                                                                                                       
  Keep this open: current main still has a plausible Responses replay failure for custom openai-responses providers                                             
  because generic Responses payloads can be unstored while replaying server-owned reasoning item IDs. Direct OpenAI                                             
  routes have a newer store-aware wrapper, but the reported custom proxy route is not covered by that direct-OpenAI-only                                        
  path.                                                                                                                                                         
